@startuml
title Gateway-Skill 多实例目标拓扑

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "终端用户" as User
node "Browser / Miniapp" as Miniapp
node "PC Agent" as PCAgent
cloud "ALB\nwss://skill.gateway.ws-url" as ALB
database "Redis 5.x" as Redis
database "MySQL 5.7.x" as MySQL

frame "Skill Server Cluster" {
  component "Skill Server S1" as S1
  component "Skill Server S2" as S2
}

frame "Gateway Cluster" {
  component "Gateway G1\nagent owner gateway" as G1
  component "Gateway G2\nskill owner gateway" as G2
  component "Gateway G3\nskill owner gateway" as G3
}

User --> Miniapp
Miniapp --> S1 : REST / WS
Miniapp --> S2 : REST / WS

PCAgent <--> G1 : WS /ws/agent

S1 --> ALB : WS /ws/internal/skill
S2 --> ALB : WS /ws/internal/skill
ALB --> G2 : WebSocket target
ALB --> G3 : WebSocket target

G1 --> Redis : PUBLISH agent:{agentId}
G2 --> Redis : SUBSCRIBE gw:relay:G2
G3 --> Redis : SUBSCRIBE gw:relay:G3
G1 --> Redis : GET/SET gw:session:skill-owner:{sessionId}
G2 --> Redis : SETEX gw:skill:owner:G2
G3 --> Redis : SETEX gw:skill:owner:G3

S1 --> Redis : PUBLISH session:{sessionId}
S2 --> Redis : SUBSCRIBE session:{sessionId}

S1 --> MySQL : Session / Message 持久化
S2 --> MySQL : Session / Message 持久化
G1 --> MySQL : Agent Registry / Auth
G2 --> MySQL : Agent Registry / Auth
G3 --> MySQL : Agent Registry / Auth

note right of Redis
Channels:
- agent:{agentId}
- session:{sessionId}
- gw:relay:{instanceId}

Keys:
- gw:skill:owner:{instanceId}
- gw:session:skill-owner:{sessionId}
- gw:skill:owners
end note

note bottom of G2
本地状态：
- local skill links
- sessionId -> linkId
end note

note bottom of G1
若本地无 skill link：
通过 Redis 查 owner gateway，
再 PUBLISH 到 gw:relay:{instanceId}
end note

@enduml
